    <stitle>International&#174; T 444E Diesel Engine Service, Model Year 1994 - 1998 - CRANKCASE, CRANKSHAFT, CONNECTING
        RODS AND PISTONS - Connecting Rods, Pistons and Piston Rings - Cleaning
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Cleaning</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Never use a caustic solution or a wire brush to clean aluminum pistons. Never use a bead blaster
                    on pistons.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Use a soap and water solution to clean the aluminum pistons. Soak the pistons, then clean
                the piston with a non-metallic brush.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Clean all piston ring grooves, connecting rod bolt holes and threads thoroughly.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">The piston pins, piston pin retainers and connecting rods may be cleaned using a suitable
                solvent.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
